== Alien Arena ==

[[File:Alienarena_screenshot1.jpg|thumb|right|150px|Alien Arena [http://red.planetarena.org/media.html more...]]]

Alien Arena is a fast paced multiplayer deathmatch game similar to ''Quake'' and ''Unreal Tournament'', but with a deep sci-fi atmosphere, lot's of shiny and weird graphics and... aliens. The engine is based on the CXR game engine, but has been rewritten to allow a lot of new features and improvements such as 32bit high-resolution textures. The physics is based on the Quake II physics, but also allows dodging. It also features single-player matches against bots. View a YouTube demo [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UlNVWIsq6dk here].

