== Nexuiz Classic ==

[[File:NexuizClassic_screenshot1.png|thumb|right|150px|Nexuiz Classic]]

Nexuiz Classic is a fast-paced 3D deathmatch game with high-end and complex graphics effects. It is intended to be played over the Internet or over a local network. Several different game types, such as classic deathmatch, team deathmatch and capture the flag are available. It also supports a single-player mode and playing against the computer. View a YouTube demo [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JhZ2_WNkr6s here].

