== Warsow ==

[[File:Warsow_screenshot1.png|thumb|right|150px|Warsow [http://www.warsow.net/media more...]]]

A fast paced open-source multiplayer shooter based on the QFusion engine. It is similar to ''Quake3'', but is set in a futuristic cartoonish world. Warsow is all about speed and movement and features known game types like ''capture the flag'' or ''instagib''. View a YouTube demo [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_RWlWlsb0yE here].

