== Xonotic ==

[[File:Xonotic_screenshot1.jpg|thumb|right|150px|Xonotic [http://www.xonotic.org/media/ more...]]]

Xonotic is a a free and fast-paced deathmatch FPS based on DarkPlaces, an advanced Quake 1 engine. It is a direct successor of the ''Nexuiz'' project and combines arena-style gameplay with rapid movement and a wide array of weapons. It could be considered most similar to ''Unreal Tournament'' and ''Quake'' at its heart, especially regarding teamplay and game mechanics. It features 18 official maps and many community contributions, has a lot of different game modes and claims to provide e-sports opportunities. It also provides an integrated statistics system called XonStat. View a YouTube demo [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9Zsp1ahGgWE here].

